latestPosts.caption:
Presenting our “Women-Owned Business of the Month”: @trisu.in , founded by the brilliant Saloni Chopra! ✨

Saloni, a third-gen jeweller from Jaipur, is redefining gold with pieces that are light, modern, and deeply meaningful. It’s a movement by women, for women, making gold evolve!

Follow @trisu.in for drops, stories, and sparkle. Jewellery made with 22kt gold vermeil, meant to be cherished for life. You won’t want to miss it! 💛

Women-Owned -Owned Business OF THE MONTH'.

Photo by Foxtale on June 11, 2025. May be an image of 1 person, smiling and text that says 'She spoke to thousands of women across India. Teachers, founders, moms and even artists. The message was clear: Gold needs to evolve.'.

Photo by Foxtale on June 11, 2025. May be an image of 1 person, necklace and text that says 'Gold was timeless. But not designed for today's woman. Saloni couldn't find anything light, modern, and meaningful so she created it.'.

Photo by Foxtale on June 11, 2025. May be an image of 1 person, jewelry and text that says 'Trisu uses 22kt gold vermeil which is 5x thicker than typical plating. Jewellery that feels precious, but lives with you through meetings, metro rides, and mandirs.'.
